       Ominous takes his seat, as dose Akron. The moment was here, arrived 
finally. It was now or never, if this meeting fell through, then Ominous was 
going to have problems.
       "Sir, are you positive he can be trusted?" Akron, ever suspicious, 
asked letting her pink eyes flutter a bit. 
       Ominous nodded as Zardus entered. He got up and smiled at the 
Commander, making sure not to touch him in fear he might absorb some of 
Zardus' energy. That wouldnt make a good start.
       "Ah, Zardus. Its been a long while, truly." He said. "This is Akron, 
she has come with me for this meeting."

--part1_f8.5d39ba9.277162d2_boundary
